==Description==
The Fighter is the most basic class. He also has the highest statistic gains in the game, due to his lack of skills.

==Main Purpose==
The Fighter provides a new-person-friendly class for incoming players.

==Statistics==
The Fighter uses primarily Power.

=== Prerequisites ===
None

=== Skills ===
None

